<a-tree-select
  allowClear
  labelInValue
  :getPopupContainer="(node) => node.parentNode"
  style="width: 100%"
  :disabled="disabled"
  :dropdownStyle="{ maxHeight: '400px', overflow: 'auto' }"
  :placeholder="placeholder"
  :loadData="asyncLoadTreeData"
  :value="treeValue"
  :treeData="treeData"
  :multiple="multiple"
  @change="onChange"
  @search="onSearch">
</a-tree-select>
